wikipedia_page.main: Kieran O'Malley (born 12 May 1988) is a British volleyball player. Born in Halifax, West Yorkshire, England, he competed for Great Britain in the men's tournament at the 2012 Summer Olympics. His team includes Gilberto Amaury de Godoy Filho, or just known as Giba.  As of 2012, he played for the Dutch team Abiant Lycurgus.
